<paragraph blockId="3.[140,1095,994,1687]" pageId="3" pageNumber="409">
<emphasis box="[179,294,995,1018]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="409">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Wall with 28±36 cancellate ribs; articular furrow of scutum deep, narrow, limbus adductorum greater than half overall height; tergum exceptionally narrow, external furrow open, distal end of spur bluntly rounded, lacking depressor muscle crests.
</paragraph>
